⍝ Replicate.tc
⍝ ════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO simple scalar/vector integer; Z nonscalar
      ⍝ inv: ¯1↓⍴Z ←→ ¯1↓⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO ← 1+2∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)    ⍝ replicate 1 or 2 times each col
      Z ← LO/B
      (¯1↓⍴Z) ≡ ¯1↓⍴B
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
